# Task Failure: Browser Initialization Issue

The task to verify the Remotion composition at http://localhost:3000 could not be completed because the browser tool is failing with a technical error: `target closed: could not read protocol padding: EOF`.

Attempts to open `http://localhost:3000`, `http://127.0.0.1:3000`, and `https://www.google.com` all failed with the same error, indicating a fundamental issue with the browser environment.
